NAME
	wize - emote a message on the wizline

SYNOPSIS
	wize <message>

DESCRIPTION
	This will send an emotion to all wizards in the game. Internally
	it is an alias to the command 'linee apprentice'. If you are 'busy W',
	that busy status will be automatically switched off (so you can hear
	the replies).

ARGUMENTS
	<message> - the emotion to send all wizards.

SEE ALSO
	busy, linee, wiz
